Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.29,0:23:27.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扣动的扳机
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.18,0:23:30.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是通向生存的选项
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.64,0:23:36.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 就要 不存在了
